                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 16.905,
                                "byte_start": 100549,
                                "byte_stop": 168258,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinion of the Court in 75-978, Du Pont against Train and the related cases will be announced by Mr. Justice Stevens."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 16.905,
                        "stop": 99.973,
